 of living righteous people","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Sulaym ibn \u2018Amir reported: The sky withheld rain, so Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Abi Sufyan and the people of Damascus sought prayers for rain. When Mu\u2019awiyah sat upon the pulpit, he said, \u201cWhere is Yazid ibn al-Aswad al-Jurashi?\u201d Then, the people called for him and he came forward cutting through the crowd.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34093,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/06\/salat-at-home-rain\/","url_meta":{"origin":6544,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Salat: Prayer at home during heavy rain, bad weather","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 6, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to order the caller to say on a cold, rainy night, \u201cSurely, pray in your homes.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 635, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 697 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43679,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/14\/prophet-always-with-abu-bakr-umar\/","url_meta":{"origin":6544,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Caliphs: The Prophet always with Abu Bakr an